rows.label: qev030401_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ganglion offer you position.
Position of respect, Uzoma Vassago![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0002
rows.name:
Pride hurt only you. Join Ganglion or die.
Join Ganglion or be food for simius.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0003
rows.name: It is simple choice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0004
rows.name:
It IS simple! Tree Clan has pride.
Cavern Clan are cowards.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0005
rows.name:
I will not betray my kin. Your threats waste time.
Will you kill me? Then kill me. No more talk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0006
rows.name: Nrrgh... As you wish![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0007
rows.name: Hm...? Who are you?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0008
rows.name:
No closer or Uzoma dies!
I will have simius tear him to pieces.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0009
rows.name: D-don't! No closer! I will kill Uzoma![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0010
rows.name:
Heh. You are brave. And strange.
Did my father ask you to come?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_JNK0010
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev030401_SEL0011
rows.name: Nod in the affirmative.

rows.label: qev030401_JNK0020
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev030401_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Uzoma how he knew.

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0011
rows.name:
It was obvious. You are reckless.
He likes this in warrior.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0012
rows.name: Tell him... I did not bend. Not to the last.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0013
rows.name:
I die with pride. Showing will of Tree Clan.
Same will that fought Cavern Clan for 10,000 suns.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0014
rows.name:
Poor simius. You are slave to Prone cowards.
My heart cries for you, brother to brother.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0015
rows.name:
This warrior will end your suffering.
Now savor your last meal![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_JNK0030
rows.name: Intervene

rows.label: qev030401_SEL0031
rows.name: Throw a sprig of kepha holly at the simius.

rows.label: qev030401_JNK0040
rows.name: Watch

rows.label: qev030401_SEL0041
rows.name: Stand back and see what unfolds.

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0016
rows.name: Kepha holly? Simius grows faint![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0017
rows.name: What...? No![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0018
rows.name: You know much, warrior.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0019
rows.name:
You are brave. But also wise. Ha ha!
You are opposite of Cavern fool![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0020
rows.name:
RAAAUGH! I need no simius!
I will kill you myself![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0021
rows.name: You die! You ALL die![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0022
rows.name:
Heh. Is death your choice? So be it.
Go, simius! Feed on his flesh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0023
rows.name: Ngh... GWAAAAUGH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030401_MSG0024
rows.name: ...You are next! All who aid Tree Clan will die![ST:wait ]
